    User[Data Scientist / Client] -->|creates| MRCR["ModelRegistry CR<br/>(v1beta1)"]
    MRCR -->|watched by| MRReconciler
    MRReconciler -->|creates/manages| MRDeploy
    MRReconciler -->|creates| MRService
    MRReconciler -->|creates| MRRoute
    MRReconciler -->|creates| MRSA
    MRReconciler -->|creates| MRRole
    MRReconciler -->|creates| MRCRB
    MRReconciler -->|creates| MRNetPol
    MRReconciler -->|creates| MRGroup
    MRReconciler -->|creates| MRSecret
    MRReconciler -->|creates| MRPostgres

    MCReconciler -->|manages| CatalogDeploy
    MCReconciler -->|manages| CatalogPostgres
    MCReconciler -->|manages| CatalogRoute
    MCReconciler -->|manages| CatalogRBAC

    SMM -->|monitors| CRD["ModelRegistry CRD"]
    SMM -->|triggers| Migration["v1alpha1 to v1beta1<br/>Migration"]

    MRCR -->|validated by| Webhooks
    CapDetect -->|informs| MRReconciler
    CapDetect -->|informs| MCReconciler

    MCReconciler -->|reads| AuthCR["Auth CR<br/>(services.platform.opendatahub.io)"]
    MCReconciler -->|reads| MRComponentCR["ModelRegistry Component CR<br/>(components.platform.opendatahub.io)"]

    RhodsOp["rhods-operator"] -->|deploys| MRReconciler

    MRDeploy -->|connects to| ExtDB["External PostgreSQL/MySQL"]
    CatalogDeploy -->|connects to| CatalogPostgres

    K8sAPI["Kubernetes API Server"] -->|TokenReview/SAR| MRDeploy
    K8sAPI -->|TokenReview/SAR| CatalogDeploy

